{"title":"【019-025】表格基础知识","slug":"hello-world2","date":"2024-01-31T11:38:03.410Z","updated":"2023-06-21T11:27:42.018Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/hello-world2.json","photos":[],"link":"","excerpt":"表格基础hello world  &nbsp;&nbsp;019 表格基础<br><br>","covers":null,"content":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=utf-8\" />\n<title>表格基础hello world</title>\n </head>\n <body>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<h3>019 表格基础</h3><br><br>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;table表格双标签，嵌套tr行双标签,tr嵌套td表格数据单元双标签。只能按照这样顺序嵌套，如果增强表现力，只能在td标签下面嵌套。\n<table>\n    <tr>\n       <td></td> \n    </tr>\n</table>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;HTML空白页，！+tab生成格式。body下输入table>tr*4>td*5，点击tab，完成格式生成。生成4行5列。\n<br><br><table>\n    <tr>\n        <td>序号</td>\n        <td>姓名</td>\n        <td>语文</td>\n        <td>数学</td>\n        <td>政治</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        <td>1</td>\n        <td>张三</td>\n        <td>80</td>\n        <td>88</td>\n        <td>70</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        <td>2</td>\n        <td>李四</td>\n        <td>90</td>\n        <td>83</td>\n        <td>99</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        <td>3</td>\n        <td>王子</td>\n        <td>86</td>\n        <td>75</td>\n        <td>89</td>\n    </tr>\n  </table> \n  <br><br> \n  &nbsp;&nbsp; <h3>020 表格属性</h3><br><br>\n  &nbsp;&nbsp;在tr下，添加th（table header cell）加粗文本双标签.\n<br><br><table>\n    <tr>\n        <th>序号</th>\n        <th>姓名</th>\n        <th>语文</th>\n        <th>数学</th>\n        <th>政治</th>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        <td>1</td>\n        <td>张三</td>\n        <td>80</td>\n        <td>88</td>\n        <td>70</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        <td>2</td>\n        <td>李四</td>\n        <td>90</td>\n        <td>83</td>\n        <td>99</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        <td>3</td>\n        <td>王子</td>\n        <td>86</td>\n        <td>75</td>\n        <td>89</td>\n    </tr>\n  </table>   &nbsp;&nbsp;<br><br>绘制表格线，在table开标签添加 border=\"\"。\n  <br><br><table border=\"1\">\n    <tr>\n        <th>序号</th>\n        <th>姓名</th>\n        <th>语文</th>\n        <th>数学</th>\n        <th>政治</th>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        <td>1</td>\n        <td>张三</td>\n        <td>80</td>\n        <td>88</td>\n        <td>70</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        <td>2</td>\n        <td>李四</td>\n        <td>90</td>\n        <td>83</td>\n        <td>99</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        <td>3</td>\n        <td>王子</td>\n        <td>86</td>\n        <td>75</td>\n        <td>89</td>\n    </tr>\n  </table> \n  <br><br> &nbsp;&nbsp;在table开标签添加 border=\"\",width=\"\",height=\"\"。\n  <br><br><table border=\"1\" width=\"500\" height=\"150\">\n    <tr>\n        <th>序号</th>\n        <th>姓名</th>\n        <th>语文</th>\n        <th>数学</th>\n        <th>政治</th>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        <td>1</td>\n        <td>张三</td>\n        <td>80</td>\n        <td>88</td>\n        <td>70</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        <td>2</td>\n        <td>李四</td>\n        <td>90</td>\n        <td>83</td>\n        <td>99</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        <td>3</td>\n        <td>王子</td>\n        <td>86</td>\n        <td>75</td>\n        <td>89</td>\n    </tr>\n  </table> \n  <br><br> cellspacing:单元格之间的距离\n  <br><br> cellpadding:单元格边框和文本间的距离\n  <br><br><table border=\"1\" width=\"500\" height=\"150\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n    <tr>\n        <th>序号</th>\n        <th>姓名</th>\n        <th>语文</th>\n        <th>数学</th>\n        <th>政治</th>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        <td>1</td>\n        <td>张三</td>\n        <td>80</td>\n        <td>88</td>\n        <td>70</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        <td>2</td>\n        <td>李四</td>\n        <td>90</td>\n        <td>83</td>\n        <td>99</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        <td>3</td>\n        <td>王子</td>\n        <td>86</td>\n        <td>75</td>\n        <td>89</td>\n    </tr>\n  </table> \n  <br><br><table border=\"1\" width=\"500\" height=\"150\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n    <tr>\n        <th>序号</th>\n        <th>姓名</th>\n        <th>语文</th>\n        <th>数学</th>\n        <th>政治</th>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        <td>1</td>\n        <td>张三</td>\n        <td>80</td>\n        <td>88</td>\n        <td>70</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        <td>2</td>\n        <td>李四</td>\n        <td>90</td>\n        <td>83</td>\n        <td>99</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        <td>3</td>\n        <td>王子</td>\n        <td>86</td>\n        <td>75</td>\n        <td>89</td>\n    </tr>\n  </table>\n  <br><br><table border=\"1\" width=\"500\" height=\"150\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" align=\"left\">\n    <tr>\n        <th>序号</th>\n        <th>姓名</th>\n        <th>语文</th>\n        <th>数学</th>\n        <th>政治</th>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        <td>1</td>\n        <td>张三</td>\n        <td>80</td>\n        <td>88</td>\n        <td>70</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        <td>2</td>\n        <td>李四</td>\n        <td>90</td>\n        <td>83</td>\n        <td>99</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        <td>3</td>\n        <td>王子</td>\n        <td>86</td>\n        <td>75</td>\n        <td>89</td>\n    </tr>\n  </table><br><br>\n  <br><br><br><br><br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;还可在里面添加bgcolor=\"\" bordercolor=\"\"<br><br>\n <table border=\"1\" width=\"500\" height=\"150\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" align=\"left\" bgcolor=\"red\" bordercolor=\"green\">\n    <tr>\n        <th>序号</th>\n        <th>姓名</th>\n        <th>语文</th>\n        <th>数学</th>\n        <th>政治</th>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        <td>1</td>\n        <td>张三</td>\n        <td>80</td>\n        <td>88</td>\n        <td>70</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        <td>2</td>\n        <td>李四</td>\n        <td>90</td>\n        <td>83</td>\n        <td>99</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        <td>3</td>\n        <td>王子</td>\n        <td>86</td>\n        <td>75</td>\n        <td>89</td>\n    </tr>\n  </table>\n  <br><br><br><br><br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp; <h3>021 表格行属性</h3><br><br>\n  &nbsp;&nbsp;表格添加高度，颜色，水平对齐，垂直对齐，tr开标签里添加height=\"\" bgcolor=\"\" align=\"left/center/right\" valign=\"top/middle/bottom\"\n  <br><br><table border=\"1\" width=\"500\" height=\"150\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" align=\"left\">\n    <tr height=\"100\">\n        <th>序号</th>\n        <th>姓名</th>\n        <th>语文</th>\n        <th>数学</th>\n        <th>政治</th>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        <td>1</td>\n        <td>张三</td>\n        <td>80</td>\n        <td>88</td>\n        <td>70</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        <td>2</td>\n        <td>李四</td>\n        <td>90</td>\n        <td>83</td>\n        <td>99</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        <td>3</td>\n        <td>王子</td>\n        <td>86</td>\n        <td>75</td>\n        <td>89</td>\n    </tr>\n  </table><br><br>\n  <br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><table border=\"1\" width=\"500\" height=\"150\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" align=\"left\" bgcolor=\"red\">\n    <tr height=\"100\" bgcolor=\"yellow\">\n        <th>序号</th>\n        <th>姓名</th>\n        <th>语文</th>\n        <th>数学</th>\n        <th>政治</th>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        <td>1</td>\n        <td>张三</td>\n        <td>80</td>\n        <td>88</td>\n        <td>70</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        <td>2</td>\n        <td>李四</td>\n        <td>90</td>\n        <td>83</td>\n        <td>99</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        <td>3</td>\n        <td>王子</td>\n        <td>86</td>\n        <td>75</td>\n        <td>89</td>\n    </tr>\n  </table>\n  <br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><table border=\"1\" width=\"500\" height=\"150\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" align=\"left\">\n    <tr height=\"100\" align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\">\n        <th>序号</th>\n        <th>姓名</th>\n        <th>语文</th>\n        <th>数学</th>\n        <th>政治</th>\n    </tr>\n    <tr align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\">\n        <td>1</td>\n        <td>张三</td>\n        <td>80</td>\n        <td>88</td>\n        <td>70</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\">\n        <td>2</td>\n        <td>李四</td>\n        <td>90</td>\n        <td>83</td>\n        <td>99</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\" >\n        <td>3</td>\n        <td>王子</td>\n        <td>86</td>\n        <td>75</td>\n        <td>89</td>\n    </tr>\n  </table><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp; <h3>022 单元格属性</h3><br><br>\n  table>tr*3>td*3d,点击tab，创建3行3列的表格。\n  <br><br><table width=\"300\" height=\"300\" border=\"1\">\n    <tr>\n        <td>1</td>\n        <td>2</td>\n        <td>3</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        <td>4</td>\n        <td>5</td>\n        <td>6</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        <td>7</td>\n        <td>8</td>\n        <td>9</td>\n    </tr>\n  </table>   \n  <br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;单元格属性，在td开标签里添加width=\" height=\"\" bgcolor=\"\" align=\"left/center/right\" valign=\"top/middle/bottom\"\n  <br><br><table width=\"300\" height=\"300\" border=\"1\">\n    <tr>\n        <td width=\"150\">1</td>\n        <td>2</td>\n        <td>3</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        <td>4</td>\n        <td>5</td>\n        <td>6</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        <td>7</td>\n        <td>8</td>\n        <td>9</td>\n    </tr>\n  </table>   \n  <br><br>\n  <br><br><table width=\"300\" height=\"300\" border=\"1\">\n    <tr>\n        <td width=\"150\" height=\"150\" bgcolor=\"red\">1</td>\n        <td>2</td>\n        <td>3</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        <td>4</td>\n        <td>5</td>\n        <td>6</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        <td>7</td>\n        <td>8</td>\n        <td>9</td>\n    </tr>\n  </table>   \n  <br><br>\n  <br><br><table width=\"300\" height=\"300\" border=\"1\">\n    <tr>\n        <td width=\"150\">1</td>\n        <td>2</td>\n        <td>3</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        <td>4</td>\n        <td>5</td>\n        <td>6</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        <td>7</td>\n        <td>8</td>\n        <td>9</td>\n    </tr>\n  </table>   \n  <br><br>\n  <br><br><table width=\"300\" height=\"300\" border=\"1\">\n    <tr>\n        <td width=\"150\" height=\"150\" bgcolor=\"red\" align=\"right\" valign=\"bottom\">1</td>\n        <td>2</td>\n        <td>3</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        <td>4</td>\n        <td>5</td>\n        <td>6</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        <td>7</td>\n        <td>8</td>\n        <td>9</td>\n    </tr>\n  </table>   \n  &nbsp;&nbsp; <h3>023 单元格合并</h3><br><br>\n  <table border=\"1\" width=\"500\" height=\"150\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n    <tr height=\"30\" align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\">\n      <td></td>\n      <td>星期一</td>\n      <td>星期二</td>\n      <td>星期三</td>\n      <td>星期四</td>\n      <td>星期五</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr height=\"30\" align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\">\n      <td>早自习</td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr height=\"30\" align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\">\n      <td>上午</td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr height=\"30\" align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\">\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr height=\"30\" align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\">\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr height=\"30\" align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\">\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr height=\"30\" align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\">\n      <td>下午</td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr height=\"30\" align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\">\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr height=\"30\" align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\">\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr height=\"30\" align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\">\n      <td></td> \n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr height=\"30\" align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\">\n      <td>晚自习</td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n    </tr>\n  </table><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;水平合并，纵向（垂直）合并,rowspan=\"\"跨几行，纵向几行合并的意思;colspan（columspan）=\"\"跨几列，横向几列合并之意。<br><br><table border=\"1\" width=\"500\" height=\"150\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n    <tr height=\"30\" bgcolor=\"deepskyblue\">\n      <th></th>\n      <th>星期一</th>\n      <th>星期二</th>\n      <th>星期三</th>\n      <th>星期四</th>\n      <th>星期五</th>\n    </tr>\n    <tr height=\"30\" align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\" bgcolor=\"skyblue\">\n      <td bgcolor=\"skyblue\">早自习</td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr height=\"30\" align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\">\n      <td rowspan=\"4\" bgcolor=\"skyblue\">上午</td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr height=\"30\" align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\" bgcolor=\"skyblue\">\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr height=\"30\" align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\">\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr height=\"30\" align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\" bgcolor=\"skyblue\">\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr height=\"30\" align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\">\n      <td rowspan=\"4\" bgcolor=\"skyblue\">下午</td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr height=\"30\" align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\" bgcolor=\"skyblue\"> \n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr height=\"30\" align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\">\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr height=\"30\" align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\" bgcolor=\"skyblue\">\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n      <td></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr height=\"30\" align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\">\n      <td bgcolor=\"skyblue\">晚自习</td>\n      <td colspan=\"5\"></td>\n    </tr>\n  </table><br><br>\n  <table border=\"1\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n    <tr height=\"30\" align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\">\n      <td colspan=\"4\">1</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr height=\"30\" align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\">\n      <td>2</td>\n      <td>3</td>\n      <td>4</td>\n      <td>5</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr height=\"30\" align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\">\n      <td rowspan=\"2\">6</td>\n      <td>7</td>\n      <td>8</td>\n      <td>9</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr height=\"30\" align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\">\n      <td>10</td>\n      <td rowspan=\"3\">11</td>\n      <td>12</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr height=\"30\" align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\">\n      <td colspan=\"2\">13</td>\n      <td>14</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr height=\"30\" align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\">\n      <td>15</td>\n      <td>16</td>\n      <td>17</td>\n    </tr>\n  </table><br><br><br><br>\n&nbsp;&nbsp; <h3>024 表格标题和结构分组</h3><br><br>\n  &nbsp;&nbsp;表格标题就是表格的大标题，默认顶部水平居中，双标签caption，位置在table和tr间。\n  <table>\n    <caption></caption>\n    <tr></tr>\n  </table><br>\n  <table border=\"1\" bordercolor=\"#ffffff\" bgcolor=\"#cde7de\" width=\"500\" height=\"150\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n    <caption><h3>成绩册</h3></caption>\n    <colgroup span=\"1\" bgcolor=\"#91c5d4\"></colgroup>\n    <thead>\n        <tr align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\">\n            <th rowspan=\"2\" bgcolor=\"skyblue\">序号</th>\n            <th colspan=\"6\" bgcolor=\"skyblue\"> by windflower</th>\n        </tr>\n        <tr bgcolor=\"skyblue\">\n            <th>姓名</th>\n            <th>语文</th>\n            <th>数学</th>\n            <th>外语</th>\n            <th>文综</th>\n            <th>总分</th>\n        </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n        <tr align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\"> \n            <th bgcolor=\"skyblue\">1</th>\n            <td>张三</td>\n            <td>90</td>\n            <td>70</td>\n            <td>80</td>\n            <td>220</td>\n            <td>460</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\">\n            <th bgcolor=\"skyblue\">2</th>\n            <td>李四</td>\n            <td>80</td>\n            <td>80</td>\n            <td>80</td>\n            <td>218</td>\n            <td>458</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\">\n            <th bgcolor=\"skyblue\">3</th>\n            <td>王子</td>\n            <td>70</td>\n            <td>80</td>\n            <td>70</td>\n            <td>220</td>\n            <td>440</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\">\n            <th bgcolor=\"skyblue\">4</th>\n            <td>陈陈</td>\n            <td>60</td>\n            <td>60</td>\n            <td>70</td>\n            <td>200</td>\n            <td>390</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\">\n            <th bgcolor=\"skyblue\">5</th>\n            <td>周周</td>\n            <td>90</td>\n            <td>80</td>\n            <td>80</td>\n            <td>210</td>\n            <td>460</td>\n        </tr>\n    </tbody>\n    <tfoot>\n        <tr align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\">\n            <th bgcolor=\"green\">说明</th>\n            <td colspan=\"6\" bgcolor=\"lightgreen\">书山有路勤为径</td>\n        </tr>\n    </tfoot>  \n  </table>\n  <br>&nbsp;&nbsp;把该表册分成三部分：thead(table head) ,tbody,tfoot,一个表格只允许1个thead,1个tfoot,多个tbody。<br><br>\n  列也可以分组，colgroup(colum group)双标签,常用于定义一整列一单元的颜色。可定义属性span=\"\"意思是多少列为1组。如果分多组，则需要多个colgroup标签。<br><br>\n  小技巧：选中内容，ctr+d,可实现多光标操作。<br><br>\n  &nbsp;&nbsp; <h3>025 颜色值和长度单位</h3><br><br>\n  &nbsp;&nbsp;颜色名称，red/green/blue;十六进制，#ff0000,00ff00,0000ff;RGB值，rgb(255，0，0，)；rgb(0，255，0；)rgb(0，0，255)<br><br>\n  <table width=\"100\">\n    <tr bgcolor=\"red\">\n      <td width=\"100px\" height=\"100px\">red</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr bgcolor=\"green\">\n      <td width=\"50px\" height=\"50px\">greem</td>\n    </tr>  \n    <tr bgcolor=\"blue\">\n        <td width=\"50px\" height=\"50px\">blue</td>\n      </tr>\n    </tr>\n  </table>\n  <table width=\"100\">\n    <tr bgcolor=\"#ff0000\">\n      <td width=\"100px\" height=\"100px\">red</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr bgcolor=\"#00ff00\">\n      <td width=\"50px\" height=\"50px\">greem</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr bgcolor=\"#0000ff\">\n      <td width=\"50px\" height=\"50px\">blue</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr bgcolor=\"rgb(255,0,0)\">\n      <td width=\"100px\" height=\"100px\">red</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr bgcolor=\"rgb(0,255,0)\">\n      <td width=\"50px\" height=\"50px\">greem</td>\n    </tr>  \n    <tr bgcolor=\"rgb(0,0,255)\">\n      <td width=\"50px\" height=\"50px\">blue</td>\n      </tr>\n    </tr>\n  </table>\n","categories":[{"name":"html","slug":"html","count":5,"path":"api/categories/html.json"}],"tags":[]}